<div class= "px-5 mt-5 content" id= "alert-page">
    <h4>ALERTS</h4>
    <p class= "mb-1">Provide contextual feedback messages for typical user actions with the handful of available and flexible alert messages.</p>
    <hr>
    <p class= "mb-1">Alerts are available for any length of text, as well as an optional dismiss button. For proper styling, use one of the eight <b>required</b> contextual classes (e.g., <span class= "text-danger">.alert-success</span>). For inline dismissal, use the alerts jQuery plugin.</p>
